{"tid":2161883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實PR又用返同一招吹鬥黃風，香港人仲會唔會上當？","createTime":"2020-08-17T20:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T03:28:24.000Z","uid":266286,"like":104,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9fc0f273ce4178970579506567d0df72d7c636","tid":2161883,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:53:08.000Z","msg":"龍門之前比你地成功拉左落神壇<br />\n只係香港人味有過被滲透分化既經驗<br />\n過左成年，各位都有目共睹<br />\n知道龍門渣哥等等既黃店做過啲乜實際既野幫過香港人<br />\n但係依家唔知道PR個腦係咪坐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地又諗住用返同一招諗住令到黃圈內耗<br />\n見到之前比PR搞到心淡既龍門成功翻身<br />\n就特登激化兩間關系原本就唔好既黃店<br />\n務求兩間黃營互咬 從而唔洗一兵一卒消滅出位黃店<br />\n手法同之前分化龍門果陣時一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇緊依個po既你<br />\n如果你唔係PR但係又屌緊兩邊黃店是但一邊既人 屌之前<br />\n諗下面對緊唔同控罪既香港人 <br />\n諗下坐緊既香港人<br />\n諗下坐完出黎既香港人<br />\n比你屌到心淡既黃店幫左佢地幾多？<br />\n你自己又幫左佢地幾多？<br />\n會唔會係自己比人帶緊風向做緊免費分化兵？<br />\n<br />\n[其實對家唔係戇鳩] 黃圈被滲透及分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地要既唔係黃色聖人圈<br />\n唔係黃色批鬥圈<br />\n更加唔係要選年度最佳龍頭黃店<br />\n香港人要既只係可以互惠互利、<br />\n同時又可以互相幫助既群體<br />\n所以只要係同路人，香港人就會支持<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n因為<br />\n<strong>我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆<br />\n我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆<br />\n我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆</strong><br />\n<br />\n係2019年6月大家耳熟能詳既宗旨，先可以令大家團結咁走落去：<br />\n<em><ins>不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力</ins></em><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461e22d6a8c97dd5f42238e4abead28fd6580621","tid":2161883,"uid":273294,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:54:07.000Z","msg":"不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfd2c7ed227d619445cb0fd7525c13d2cc77e87","tid":2161883,"uid":79410,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:56:51.000Z","msg":"西灣河屌丘品<br />\n理大屌蘋果<br />\n71屌立場<br />\n影唔到又話你影唔到<br />\n影到又你影到<br />\n藍絲分化狗冇事化小事。小事化大事。大事化巨事<br />\n但又唔見佢哋開post屌藍店"},{"pid":"0bab1e27a496ffcc196099483869a21f6c551d68","tid":2161883,"uid":97716,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:56:57.000Z","msg":"你不如cap 呢句去渣家軍到啦屌<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><strong>我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆</strong></span><br />\n睇下佢地點覆你？<br />\n佢地分化咗成年啦"},{"pid":"f051c71740cf628537fe79a70b3637a025d902b0","tid":2161883,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcfd2c7ed227d619445cb0fd7525c13d2cc77e87","tid":2161883,"uid":79410,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:56:51.000Z","msg":"西灣河屌丘品<br />\n理大屌蘋果<br />\n71屌立場<br />\n影唔到又話你影唔到<br />\n影到又你影到<br />\n藍絲分化狗冇事化小事。小事化大事。大事化巨事<br />\n但又唔見佢哋開post屌藍店"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:57:59.000Z","msg":"駁唔刀"},{"pid":"4058668a0a6a3a643b51d76f3d94b307c663cf3d","tid":2161883,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:58:38.000Z","msg":"見到D撚樣仲分緊邊個黃D, 做過D咩, 真係得啖笑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2151263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2151263</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a16a500f233ea2d91388fcc1026bb48fb01984e4","tid":2161883,"uid":318505,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fcfd2c7ed227d619445cb0fd7525c13d2cc77e87","tid":2161883,"uid":79410,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:56:51.000Z","msg":"西灣河屌丘品<br />\n理大屌蘋果<br />\n71屌立場<br />\n影唔到又話你影唔到<br />\n影到又你影到<br />\n藍絲分化狗冇事化小事。小事化大事。大事化巨事<br />\n但又唔見佢哋開post屌藍店"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:59:15.000Z","msg":"講到屌渣家軍分化嘅人有亂咁屌埋以上嘅事<br />\nGoodest logic"},{"pid":"b19fc5f929440ca1751962cde84ddb06c03914e4","tid":2161883,"uid":97716,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a16a500f233ea2d91388fcc1026bb48fb01984e4","tid":2161883,"uid":318505,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fcfd2c7ed227d619445cb0fd7525c13d2cc77e87","tid":2161883,"uid":79410,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:56:51.000Z","msg":"西灣河屌丘品<br />\n理大屌蘋果<br />\n71屌立場<br />\n影唔到又話你影唔到<br />\n影到又你影到<br />\n藍絲分化狗冇事化小事。小事化大事。大事化巨事<br />\n但又唔見佢哋開post屌藍店"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:59:15.000Z","msg":"講到屌渣家軍分化嘅人有亂咁屌埋以上嘅事<br />\nGoodest logic"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:00:48.000Z","msg":"渣家軍=大條道理<br />\n良心理性黃= PR<br />\n笑撚死"},{"pid":"cb4beec4317fcaf4d2c3fc6efc5e16b43f3acc0f","tid":2161883,"uid":266286,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:03:47.000Z","msg":"不如諗下點解得我地會成日有分化？<br />\n大家回想下幾時見到空姐牛肉飯屌楊明燉湯唔夠藍或者偽藍？<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>無呀嘛</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f06d11e34febea8b9db6f339ec756a85b5f29dc","tid":2161883,"uid":79410,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cb4beec4317fcaf4d2c3fc6efc5e16b43f3acc0f","tid":2161883,"uid":266286,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:03:47.000Z","msg":"不如諗下點解得我地會成日有分化？<br />\n大家回想下幾時見到空姐牛肉飯屌楊明燉湯唔夠藍或者偽藍？<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>無呀嘛</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:06:59.000Z","msg":"因為黃圈冇錢請PR<br />\n屌眾志<br />\n屌黃之峰<br />\n屌攬炒巴<br />\n總之有位就入。冇位都要鑽開個窿嚟入"},{"pid":"155c2905bf56e5567fe1284934946bcd029141cc","tid":2161883,"uid":47509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:07:33.000Z","msg":"不分化呀"},{"pid":"ffdefbd52ab59a071b3d37fafcb7da0e21ca9b4b","tid":2161883,"uid":36551,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:08:13.000Z","msg":"咁事實係無論龍門做啲乜，都會俾渣狗同閪門雞喺FB狙擊抽水喎，到底係邊個分化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414d3cbe43a59298b4e14e98c2d83b13de8e65bd","tid":2161883,"uid":47810,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ffdefbd52ab59a071b3d37fafcb7da0e21ca9b4b","tid":2161883,"uid":36551,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:08:13.000Z","msg":"咁事實係無論龍門做啲乜，都會俾渣狗同閪門雞喺FB狙擊抽水喎，到底係邊個分化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:09:20.000Z","msg":"按樓主標準你已經係鬥緊黃。"},{"pid":"9b258de88a74d101db402faec7824b83b0579043","tid":2161883,"uid":266286,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:25:39.000Z","msg":"渣哥同龍門之間既恩怨<br />\n無論真係PR引戰好<br />\n定係被PR成功帶風向既手足都好<br />\n只要參與引戰既人越少<br />\nPR搧風點火既效用就會越細<br />\n竟然PR係不可抗力既因素<br />\n就只有各位手足做好自己本分<br />\n睇清楚你地做緊既野係咪PR喜聞樂見既<br />\n唔好比佢地再一次帶到批鬥既風向！<br />\n<br />\n難聽啲講句：<br />\n龍門同渣哥同你地有親咩？<br />\n佢地打交關你咩事姐<br />\n佢地做到自己本份咪得囉屌！"},{"pid":"7cfe6c174b448d08deb4e020fcb1026a0215c0af","tid":2161883,"uid":365130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:27:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5a7da46878e792be869e02ffc3ec0bebb717f39","tid":2161883,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2439477be0259c2409cb8518090d19832b0fe6","tid":2161883,"uid":143183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:31:41.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"09fd586bbc14f0846b2b656ac82597e445a1c381","tid":2161883,"uid":309443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:39:42.000Z","msg":"推 雖然渣狗今次係衰 但係希望黃圈停分化"},{"pid":"551f46f8fbaf47248e980400250dd017575001e4","tid":2161883,"uid":270803,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:50:13.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔明<br />\n<br />\n明知有pr<br />\n<br />\n明知有一毛<br />\n<br />\n由之前講唔好捉鬼， 到今日講唔好鬥黃<br />\n<br />\n全部都講左好多好多次， 講左好多個月<br />\n<br />\n我睇每件事就好簡單<br />\n<br />\nkeep住幫手&gt; 幫過手&gt; 咩都唔做&gt; 藍絲<br />\n<br />\n你話渣哥呀， 龍門呀呢d屬於邊種？<br />\n<br />\n明明咁多藍絲藍店紅店等你去鬥<br />\n<br />\n係度嘈嘈嘈"},{"pid":"b245813893bbc0d026a59579bdde2e8f3d9f035c","tid":2161883,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:52:52.000Z","msg":"Miss pun 賣手足還押都可以原諒，點解要追屌深黄渣哥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5266023269ced084debbd9b0588b069c4a57331","tid":2161883,"uid":208834,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:59:50.000Z","msg":"渣哥自己攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n渣哥又咪係屌藍就細細聲<br />\n屌龍門就有位上盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆頭都好抽水<br />\n<br />\n今次佢自己公關災難<br />\n唔撚理黃唔黃<br />\n大把人唔去食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比你del咗comment 嬲到七彩仲點幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你幾時見過人地藍店del自己的藍絲食客comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好講pr啦 渣哥自己帶頭分化你唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fae4c12c0f842683e8d5c307284f97addacd74","tid":2161883,"uid":270073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:01:57.000Z","msg":"講得係有道理，但另一方面，班黃店自己都要做好本份，下下抽水、搞小圈子真係爭唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己就幫襯開小店，就算只係擺隻pepe都係一種姿態。"},{"pid":"38996fcfa5f1cdbb09a1cdbef7fb1eac27b1f7c7","tid":2161883,"uid":47810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49fae4c12c0f842683e8d5c307284f97addacd74","tid":2161883,"uid":270073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:01:57.000Z","msg":"講得係有道理，但另一方面，班黃店自己都要做好本份，下下抽水、搞小圈子真係爭唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己就幫襯開小店，就算只係擺隻pepe都係一種姿態。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:08:05.000Z","msg":"你仲鬥黃？ 按樓主標準你已經係鬥緊黃！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ac1537978e13fefdd6de6238c74e9812c111cf","tid":2161883,"uid":28264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:13:33.000Z","msg":"呢架咁既情況香港人只係識同一陣營內鬥<br />\n老鄧果一句真係沒撚講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf1d6de767c27f4083863eef533c964f2068b4c","tid":2161883,"uid":147226,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:29:12.000Z","msg":"[任務次序] 連去美心MX facebook 俾個負評都懶，但你班人就寫千字文批鬥黃店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2160088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2160088</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d02e385bca7724f1ae0f3d9f4372091950664b30","tid":2161883,"uid":34764,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:35:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2161767/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2161767/page/1</a><br />\n樓主你可唔可以認清最落力分化黃圈係邊班人？<br />\n你好似乜都唔清唔楚就鬧哂批評渣家軍既人係pr五毛<br />\n係咪渣家軍班人出書鬧龍門 繼續日日抽龍門水 都要繼續用不完美可接受黎縱容佢地？ <br />\n你可唔可以睇哂所有事既來龍去脈先學人出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真你先似d帶風向既pr"},{"pid":"6ac63ce3f780d701cbdab0b31d3765df551a09ca","tid":2161883,"uid":120480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:38:25.000Z","msg":"渣狗block曬啲人，所以啲人依家上曬連登嘈囉"},{"pid":"99271b2a894fd51e6bd370628f56a94514a5da78","tid":2161883,"uid":98313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b825d8ef5cfcfd3f8070acea48abbabbd114f878","tid":2161883,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:41:00.000Z","msg":"推 香港民研有調查，問大家是否贊成泛民繼續出任議員 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2160944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2160944</a>"},{"pid":"e24d3a9bd3d273b7a027c36b1e45a8efa1051e9b","tid":2161883,"uid":277536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:44:45.000Z","msg":"渣狗屌人就大條道理+講得好<br />\n渣狗被屌時就大家唔好鬥黃"},{"pid":"f755e87fadc9d214d778a7a291d8d8f00f5ceeaa","tid":2161883,"uid":166646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:51:09.000Z","msg":"有空鬥藍啦 又係甘龍門之前中過計 引戰狗 間間做晒聖人好唔好 而家政治立場變撚左做人道德。香港人都幾得閒  鬥鬥鬥"},{"pid":"061748249039df7f006342053fe1fbe0409fdb70","tid":2161883,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffdefbd52ab59a071b3d37fafcb7da0e21ca9b4b","tid":2161883,"uid":36551,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:08:13.000Z","msg":"咁事實係無論龍門做啲乜，都會俾渣狗同閪門雞喺FB狙擊抽水喎，到底係邊個分化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:53:49.000Z","msg":"你過界，我過界...."},{"pid":"c9fc4d5a98feab86b050161998b7bfceabe6ce1f","tid":2161883,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e24d3a9bd3d273b7a027c36b1e45a8efa1051e9b","tid":2161883,"uid":277536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:44:45.000Z","msg":"渣狗屌人就大條道理+講得好<br />\n渣狗被屌時就大家唔好鬥黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:55:33.000Z","msg":"講到呢幾年嚟好似得渣狗事件咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a900f197fd83d90bc3dedcbdbf91f6d81cdf0c","tid":2161883,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5188cb30d0ffc3820de840497298c6bd693628","tid":2161883,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3acedb7ba631f93ab33b4157d7236239409156","tid":2161883,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e9fc0f273ce4178970579506567d0df72d7c636","tid":2161883,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:53:08.000Z","msg":"龍門之前比你地成功拉左落神壇<br />\n只係香港人味有過被滲透分化既經驗<br />\n過左成年，各位都有目共睹<br />\n知道龍門渣哥等等既黃店做過啲乜實際既野幫過香港人<br />\n但係依家唔知道PR個腦係咪坐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地又諗住用返同一招諗住令到黃圈內耗<br />\n見到之前比PR搞到心淡既龍門成功翻身<br />\n就特登激化兩間關系原本就唔好既黃店<br />\n務求兩間黃營互咬 從而唔洗一兵一卒消滅出位黃店<br />\n手法同之前分化龍門果陣時一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇緊依個po既你<br />\n如果你唔係PR但係又屌緊兩邊黃店是但一邊既人 屌之前<br />\n諗下面對緊唔同控罪既香港人 <br />\n諗下坐緊既香港人<br />\n諗下坐完出黎既香港人<br />\n比你屌到心淡既黃店幫左佢地幾多？<br />\n你自己又幫左佢地幾多？<br />\n會唔會係自己比人帶緊風向做緊免費分化兵？<br />\n<br />\n[其實對家唔係戇鳩] 黃圈被滲透及分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地要既唔係黃色聖人圈<br />\n唔係黃色批鬥圈<br />\n更加唔係要選年度最佳龍頭黃店<br />\n香港人要既只係可以互惠互利、<br />\n同時又可以互相幫助既群體<br />\n所以只要係同路人，香港人就會支持<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n因為<br />\n<strong>我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆<br />\n我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆<br />\n我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆</strong><br />\n<br />\n係2019年6月大家耳熟能詳既宗旨，先可以令大家團結咁走落去：<br />\n<em><ins>不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力</ins></em><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T23:19:09.000Z","msg":"點解咁多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4216fbb115fb7dc5a87cf15a2ce361079601fbd","tid":2161883,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T23:59:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7661e921696e270a96001a1cad8caa0f7bb585c","tid":2161883,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:00:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8d1c927a7ec3784ce0369af1bcef4b8639a31d1","tid":2161883,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:00:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66e4331d542a6ddbe4de273d97c08c8f164e12fb","tid":2161883,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:00:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f08e3706391e509c40c6962697a59a0c3610998b","tid":2161883,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b258de88a74d101db402faec7824b83b0579043","tid":2161883,"uid":266286,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T21:25:39.000Z","msg":"渣哥同龍門之間既恩怨<br />\n無論真係PR引戰好<br />\n定係被PR成功帶風向既手足都好<br />\n只要參與引戰既人越少<br />\nPR搧風點火既效用就會越細<br />\n竟然PR係不可抗力既因素<br />\n就只有各位手足做好自己本分<br />\n睇清楚你地做緊既野係咪PR喜聞樂見既<br />\n唔好比佢地再一次帶到批鬥既風向！<br />\n<br />\n難聽啲講句：<br />\n龍門同渣哥同你地有親咩？<br />\n佢地打交關你咩事姐<br />\n佢地做到自己本份咪得囉屌！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:01:07.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"87ecc9781e545246221c03af5b6c038ef4d9aa72","tid":2161883,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab3acedb7ba631f93ab33b4157d7236239409156","tid":2161883,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e9fc0f273ce4178970579506567d0df72d7c636","tid":2161883,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:53:08.000Z","msg":"龍門之前比你地成功拉左落神壇<br />\n只係香港人味有過被滲透分化既經驗<br />\n過左成年，各位都有目共睹<br />\n知道龍門渣哥等等既黃店做過啲乜實際既野幫過香港人<br />\n但係依家唔知道PR個腦係咪坐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地又諗住用返同一招諗住令到黃圈內耗<br />\n見到之前比PR搞到心淡既龍門成功翻身<br />\n就特登激化兩間關系原本就唔好既黃店<br />\n務求兩間黃營互咬 從而唔洗一兵一卒消滅出位黃店<br />\n手法同之前分化龍門果陣時一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇緊依個po既你<br />\n如果你唔係PR但係又屌緊兩邊黃店是但一邊既人 屌之前<br />\n諗下面對緊唔同控罪既香港人 <br />\n諗下坐緊既香港人<br />\n諗下坐完出黎既香港人<br />\n比你屌到心淡既黃店幫左佢地幾多？<br />\n你自己又幫左佢地幾多？<br />\n會唔會係自己比人帶緊風向做緊免費分化兵？<br />\n<br />\n[其實對家唔係戇鳩] 黃圈被滲透及分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地要既唔係黃色聖人圈<br />\n唔係黃色批鬥圈<br />\n更加唔係要選年度最佳龍頭黃店<br />\n香港人要既只係可以互惠互利、<br />\n同時又可以互相幫助既群體<br />\n所以只要係同路人，香港人就會支持<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n因為<br />\n<strong>我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆<br />\n我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆<br />\n我地係無本錢分化，無本錢割蓆</strong><br />\n<br />\n係2019年6月大家耳熟能詳既宗旨，先可以令大家團結咁走落去：<br />\n<em><ins>不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力</ins></em><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T23:19:09.000Z","msg":"點解咁多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:03:44.000Z","msg":"有為好多人覺得渣哥有問題，要做死佢<br />\n好笑，美心同牛肺飯未死，黃圈自己鬥死左"},{"pid":"74b0973f1865e1b817a3af293a0dca854a388db9","tid":2161883,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:09:36.000Z","msg":"渣哥單嘢 唔只係講緊佢同龍門<br />\n係佢態度唔好 問兩問就屌鳩人<br />\n平心靜氣傾唔得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0d373f2598e7e4d26d0f6901eb549dcc5bf45d","tid":2161883,"uid":109670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:10:40.000Z","msg":"唔通渣狗就係最大既pr公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bba5dc9f1377aab32ebbfb080cdc2fd00a7902d","tid":2161883,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁得閒整合點鬥點鬥<br />\n不如花精神追擊對家好過啦"},{"pid":"f5d8eb1a2688ed1a8bfa486dcbe1400fc3f26396","tid":2161883,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:12:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d1b5241c2a6e3b210dfb9082984e92a6f96a1b4","tid":2161883,"uid":196292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bba5dc9f1377aab32ebbfb080cdc2fd00a7902d","tid":2161883,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁得閒整合點鬥點鬥<br />\n不如花精神追擊對家好過啦"},"citedBy":2